{"tid":1379261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[小心] 發現開始無申請既網媒混入傳媒前線，各傳媒朋友入黎","createTime":"2019-07-28T18:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T18:45:02.000Z","uid":23815,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"05794578f3eb920de4e385bf70066b700be75067","tid":1379261,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:22:19.000Z","msg":"琴晚我老母話何俊仁同肥佬黎係元朗茶記食飯同係現場指揮 ，仲比左張圖我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EqoMmdM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEqoMmdM.png&h=5a4faf9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://但HK.on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BD%86HK.on.cc&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyyz%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=e332beca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">但HK.on.cc</a> 並無仼何報導關於佢兩個<br />\n<br />\n仲有另一張大公報既圖 係何俊仁現場指揮 <br />\n又係揾唔到<br />\n<br />\n去到google image 發現係大陸網 &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">觀察者&rdquo;</span>既假新聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbrJ7U4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbrJ7U4.png&h=4e319785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我呢兩日睇<span style=\"color: red;\">Live</span> 發現有白衫藍字 左心口寫 &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">觀察者</span>&rdquo; 既人企係傳媒報導開live既位置 （琴晚元朗一定有）<br />\n<br />\n岩先隔離post亦有藍媒 &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">沉默電台</span>&rdquo; post左前線既gear相<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>各位傳媒朋友，我相信大家為左香港既聲音，不妨向奇怪既傳媒去望一望大家身邊既傳媒證，如果有人偽造，可以揭發，以免有人係傳媒群中搞事，令報導真相既你地受害</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6393df1b750a8145a4ffdcb751677d5c0a0f078c","tid":1379261,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /